'''''The Lost Jedi''''' is a series of "choose your own adventure" style books published from [[1993]] to [[1994]]. Written by [[Paul Cockburn]] and published by [[Boxtree]], the books were only available in the United Kingdom. The series included two books, ''[[Jedi Dawn]]'' and ''[[The Bounty Hunter]]'', which were both later collected in ''[[The Lost Jedi Adventure Game Book]]''.<ref name="LJ">''[[The Lost Jedi Adventure Game Book]]''</ref>

